::Striker::

Striker's eyes widen slightly as Spears kisses him, the Maximal tightening 
his hold on her. He smiles, resuming walking toward the valley where they had 
been headed.

He looks into his optics, nearly tripping over a root due to not looking 
where he was going. He keeps his balance, smiling as he continues to walk.
